{
  "id": "create_concept@1",
  "version": "1.0",
  "env_id": "openmrs_env@0.1",
  "description": "Create a new medical concept in the OpenMRS Dictionary with the following specifications:\n- Fully Specified Name: 'Toluene Exposure'\n- Synonym: 'Methylbenzene exp'\n- Class: Diagnosis\n- Datatype: N/A\n- Description: 'Occupational exposure to toluene solvent'\n\nEnsure the concept is saved and active.",
